{"tid":1970524,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入] 呢個故事教訓我，真係唔可以亂咁殺生","createTime":"2020-04-13T08:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T02:40:15.000Z","uid":240251,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6991589e6d6ac74ee775aea94c0d5b3e58e6369","tid":1970524,"uid":240251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n半年前我睇睇下電腦<br />\n發覺有隻蟲在moon上面移動<br />\n我有佛心  內心鬥爭左好耐<br />\n到底我殺唔殺佢好<br />\n最後我好殘忍咁捽死左佢<br />\n<br />\n之後惡夢就開始<br />\n唔知係咪蟲既密度高過led moon既密度<br />\n成條蟲屍俾我壓左入去個moon入面<br />\n然後我無論噴酒精點樣抹<br />\n隻蟲都好似侏羅紀公園果d琥珀標本咁凝固住<br />\n<br />\n呢半年間<br />\n周不時睇睇下野  就alert到蟲屍既存在 同埋我曾經對佢既殺戳<br />\n好痛苦<br />\n<br />\n畫面如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asK5pzh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasK5pzh.jpg&h=cb5449b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以大家千祈唔好殺生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 有冇人知點整走佢"},{"pid":"fafbd8f7ebce4763dc3e43a2a0a363149d1ebca5","tid":1970524,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb8ca599268d209ffdf83003ff34608b0fc5c1b","tid":1970524,"uid":90244,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"你咪當係滑鼠遊標囉"},{"pid":"42620c4c45483a8e055a0aaa2f856f15e6233f1c","tid":1970524,"uid":120040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"睇緊你個post醒起我都有隻蟻爬咗入個mon死咗 同問<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTFkdwT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTFkdwT.png&h=e8417cb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d282bdd93556ad0bff3248444a58d47d9770184","tid":1970524,"uid":212441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-